  <h2 id="tips">Tips for Avoiding Surprise Charges <a href="#tips">#</a></h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Always specify in your request</strong> that you prefer electronic copies if possible</li>
    <li><strong>Ask for an estimate</strong> of the volume of documents before the department proceeds</li>
    <li><strong>Be specific</strong> in your request to avoid receiving more documents than you need</li>
    <li><strong>Check if information is proactively published</strong> on the department's website (free access)</li>
  </ul>

